title: NFL ATL: Minicamp winners & losers
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Minicamp winners & losers
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- debate the winners and losers from the 2014 edition of minicamps. The heroic foursome also react to the latest news from around the league, including the Tom Brady and New York Jets' playbook fiasco, and the Atlanta Falcons’ new backup quarterback.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
